'''干擾因子'''（英語：'''Confounder'''、'''Confound'''、或'''Confounding variable'''），又稱為'''共變因'''、'''干擾變量'''，在統計學和因果關係中，是指會同時影響兩個[[變數|變數]]的變數。在不嚴謹的語境下，干擾因子也可以指所有'''未知變數'''（英語：'''lurking variable'''），包括[[中介變因|中介變因]]、和[[對撞變因|對撞變因]]。干擾因子會造成[[偽關係|偽關係]]，是[[相關不蘊涵因果|相關不蘊涵因果]]的原因之一。<ref name="Pearl 2009">Pearl, J., (2009). [[Simpson's_Paradox|Simpson's Paradox]], Confounding, and Collapsibility In ''Causality: Models, Reasoning and Inference'' (2nd ed.). New York : Cambridge University Press.</ref><ref>{{cite journal | last1 = VanderWeele | first1 = T.J. | last2 = Shpitser | first2 = I. | year = 2013 | title = On the definition of a confounder | url =https://archive.org/details/sim_annals-of-statistics_2013-02_41_1/page/196| journal = Annals of Statistics | volume = 41 | issue = 1| pages = 196–220 | doi=10.1214/12-aos1058| pmid = 25544784 | pmc = 4276366 | arxiv = 1304.0564 }}</ref><ref name="Greenland Pearl Robbins 1999">{{cite journal | last1 = Greenland | first1 = S. | last2 = Robins | first2 = J. M. | last3 = Pearl | first3 = J. | year = 1999 | title = Confounding and Collapsibility in Causal Inference | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_statistical-science_1999-02_14_1/page/29 | doi = 10.1214/ss/1009211805 | journal = Statistical Science | volume = 14 | issue = 1| pages = 29–46 | doi-access = free }}</ref>

